WinLamb

https://github.com/rodrigocfd/winlamb

A modern C++11 object-oriented library to write native Windows programs.


This library is explained in depth in this article:
https://www.codeproject.com/Articles/1184175/WinLamb-using-Cplusplus-lambdas-to-handle-Win-mess


